      "id": "tutorial-create-repo-01",
      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.409686,
      "replayEndSec": 11.760396,
      "narrationText": "让我们在服务器上创建一个 2 GB 的加密仓库。仓库静态时是一个单一加密文件，挂载后变成拥有独立 Docker 守护进程和独立应用数据的文件夹，与服务器上的其他一切完全隔离。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-create-repo/tutorial-create-repo-01.d3af171d.mp3",
      "textHash": "d3af171d647dee6e195604f4ece88dbe7997272519bde84a7e61488b6876fd1a",
      "audioDurationSec": 17.632653,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-create-repo/tutorial-create-repo-01-after.73ddf470.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.787755,
      "afterTextHash": "73ddf47042304ddf5c7c87d70cb1ca2eadcba5431a4860daa32acb9768dcc891"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-create-repo-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 11.760396,
      "replayEndSec": 17.238181,
      "narrationText": "让我们列出机器上的仓库，确认新仓库已注册。从这里开始，仓库可以在 VS Code 中打开、部署、fork 或备份，全都从笔记本完成。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-create-repo/tutorial-create-repo-02.e102d567.mp3",
      "textHash": "e102d567f7b763b4993c2b0d9396c37e720a6fe130de57cf41b0c10f4a1e2af6",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.635918,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-create-repo/tutorial-create-repo-02-after.d5e5f2f7.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.586122,
      "afterTextHash": "d5e5f2f72b5cb44597662f1173acf8ffc695c0815bbbb618d544bfec6e53327e"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-create-repo-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 17.238181,
      "replayEndSec": 21.33289,
      "narrationText": "一个实用选项：用这条命令直接在 VS Code 中打开 repo。我们这里不会启动编辑器，但它会通过 SSH 建立一个进入 repo 的远程会话，让你可以编辑其中的文件。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-create-repo/tutorial-create-repo-03.787959ed.mp3",
      "textHash": "787959ed09fe7eb80a0b43491cd9f5d4574527ff141b7f2ced99c7ad690e0b73",
      "audioDurationSec": 16.274286,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-create-repo/tutorial-create-repo-03-after.a481e2d3.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 5.564082,
      "afterTextHash": "a481e2d33d17ff9a404f4e1ff5c190cbd5d3e072962f9f15d96924f34f42d555"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "textHash": "54541e82e46a92f6235ab86e335d61f229a12f3a20e6812cc7893bbfe1bede2e",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-create-repo/intro.54541e82.mp3",
      "narrationText": "让我们来创建你的第一个仓库！它静态时是一个加密文件，挂载后变成一个完全隔离的环境。",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.594286
    },
    {
      "id": "file-on-disk",
      "textHash": "ef73d0ea7edfc2eec470500294fdaf7f40ac99c15781883a598cd41e9b0e8041",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-create-repo/file-on-disk.ef73d0ea.mp3",
      "narrationText": "在磁盘上它是单一加密镜像。挂载后，你会获得专用的 Docker 守护进程、保存在加密卷内的应用数据，以及不会与服务器上其他任何东西冲突的环回 IP。",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.445714
    },
